Maijoor Says Europe Needs More Budget Control Over EU Members

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-10-13T14:17:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/maijoor-says-europe-needs-more-budget-control-over-eu-members.html
Steven Maijoor, chairman of the
European Securities and Markets Authority, called for more
central control over the budgets and economic programs of
European Union member states. He spoke at a conference in Lisbon
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anabela Reis in Lisbon at 
